  <brief_title>A Double Blind Placebo Controlled Study to Assess the Efficacy on Joint Damage in RA Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>FK506 Phase 4 Study: A Double Blind Placebo Controlled Study to Assess the Efficacy on Joint Damage in RA Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
